in each match, making every win and every loss understandable. Once you understand the core mechanics with a few quick matches, it's all down to skill! Even when you’re losing, there’s always an opportunity to strike back and win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896570/extras/a40c2959681cdac5b1cd45ce120bbc68.poster.avif?t=1771878540\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896570/extras/a40c2959681cdac5b1cd45ce120bbc68.webm?t=1771878540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896570/extras/a40c2959681cdac5b1cd45ce120bbc68.mp4?t=1771878540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
